        "created_at": "2017-11-11T22:21:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A bit surprised that you seem to have appreciated the '05 Comte Armand so much. Paul opened a bottle blind after we tasted the '15s together last year and I was shocked at how dominated by high toast oak it was, all espresso and bacon fat. Did the wood seem integrated to you?</p>",
